of funeral homes, started trading under LWNGF. The American
Stock Exchange and the Chicago Board Options Exchange have
begun trading options on the common stock of Cellular
Communications Inc., a New York owner and operator of phone
systems, under CMQ. The Amex also began trading options on
the shares of CoreStates Financial Corp., the Philadelphia
bank holding company, under CFQ.
