   Media General Inc., a Richmond, Va.-based broadcast,
cable-TV and publishing company, said J. Stewart Bryan III
was named chairman, president and chief executive officer,
effective July 1.
   Mr. Bryan, 52 years old, is currently chief operating
officer of the company and publisher of its Richmond
